        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "The 'ladder': one rook cuts off the 7th rank, the other delivers mate on the 8th. 1.Rb7 forces the black king onto the back rank (Kd8 or Kf8 — both lose), and 2.Ra8# completes the staircase. Two rooks corner the king without any king help needed, which is why this mate is so quick.",
          "target": "'阶梯'：一个车切断第7横线，另一个在第8横线将死。1.Rb7 迫使黑王回到底线（Kd8 或 Kf8 — 均输），2.Ra8# 完成阶梯。双车无需王的帮助即可将王逼入角落，这就是为什么这个将死如此迅速。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "With your king in front of a 7th-rank pawn (not a- or h-file) and your rook free, build a 'bridge' on the 4th rank (Rc4!), then march your king out behind it. The defending rook eventually runs out of useful checks and the pawn promotes.",
          "target": "当你的王位于第7横线兵的前方（非 a 或 h 线）且你的车自由时，在第4横线建造一个'桥'（Rc4!），然后让王从桥后走出。防守方的车最终会耗尽有效的将军，兵升变。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "As the defender, plant your rook on the third rank to keep the enemy king off the 6th. The instant the pawn pushes to e6, swing the rook behind the pawn (…Rh1) and check from the long side. Draw.",
          "target": "作为防守方，将你的车放在第三横线以阻止敌王进入第6横线。一旦兵推进到 e6，立即将车移到兵后（…Rh1）并从长边将军。和棋。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Defender's rook attacks the a-pawn from the side along the 6th rank, the defender's king cuts the long side. The white king can never both shield the pawn and escape the side checks — drawn.",
          "target": "防守方的车从第6横线侧面攻击 a 兵，防守方的王切断长边。白王永远无法既保护兵又避开侧面的将军 — 和棋。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "With your king *in front of* the pawn on the 6th rank, you win by gaining the opposition (kings face off with one square between them, opponent to move). If the defender takes the opposition with the king on the key squares first, the position is drawn.",
          "target": "当你的王位于第6横线兵的前方时，通过获得对王（两王相隔一格，轮到对方走棋）即可获胜。如果防守方的王抢先占据关键格获得对王，则局面为和棋。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "With a rook-pawn whose promotion square does *not* match your bishop's color, the defender hides in the corner. Any approach by the strong side ends in stalemate (push the pawn here and the black king has no legal move). Memorise the corner colors before trading into this ending.",
          "target": "当车兵的升变格与你的象颜色不同时，防守方可以躲在角落。进攻方的任何逼近都会导致和棋（在此推进兵，黑王将无合法走法）。在进入此残局前，请先记住角落的颜色。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Study chess in your vault. Embed positions, study openings and endgames, browse World Championship games, annotate PGNs, and explore Lichess opening statistics.",
          "target": "在你的棋库中学习国际象棋。嵌入棋局、研究开局与残局、浏览世界冠军赛棋局、注释PGN文件，并探索Lichess开局统计数据。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Paste a FEN string below. The block is inserted when you confirm.",
          "target": "在下方粘贴FEN字符串。确认后将插入棋盘。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "description",
          "source": "Paste a Lichess game URL or game ID below.",
          "target": "在下方粘贴Lichess对局URL或对局ID。"
        },
        {
